name: Catholic Community Service In-home Support of Northeast Kansas

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Catholic Community Service In-home Support of Northeast Kansas is a In Home Supportive Care provider based in Lenexa, KS. From 2023-06 through 2024-04, this provider received $137K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 237 beneficiaries, billing 1 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 100% of billing is concentrated in S5125 (S5125), indicating significant specialization in this service.
